{"id":"94bb1833-4067-4d32-9629-58f2d135574a","name":"The Child Isn't Yours ","description":"<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong>UNAVOIDABLE NTR:</strong></span></h1><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong>ALREADY CUCKED</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 57);\">After defeating </span><span style=\"color: rgb(190, 125, 255);\">Magima</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 57);\">, </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 190, 0);\">your girlfriend, Ember</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 57);\">, had to be brought to the hospital to flush her system of the spiked tea and whatever magic was placed on her.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 57);\">For about 6 months, </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 170, 0);\">Ember</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 57);\"> was recovering in a women's hospital, and visitation from you was blocked due to the urgency of the treatment she needed. No distractions from any visitors.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 57);\">However, </span><span style=\"color: rgb(197, 107, 255);\">Magima</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 57);\"> has a surprise for you. She wants to bury the hatchet, after she tells you </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 161, 223);\">one last thing.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>The world of Trendia is vast.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>Here is a map to help you navigate:</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/vUo9MzLlMkZ8YgoTAE5wr.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">I decided to make this sequel after a certain creator stole my image. Now here's a sequel. Enjoy part 1 here:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/02216ba3-1866-4714-8ab0-e65cb746c057_character-youre-too-weak-to-save-her\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong>You're too weak to save her.</strong></span></a></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"D6DLt4Nz_gU6BtBYGLoZc.webp","creator":"Directive_43_Appraiser","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🔮 Magical","👭 Multiple","👤 AnyPOV","💔 Angst","❤️‍🩹 Fluff","🛸 Sci-Fi"],"chats":2852,"messages":44578,"created_at":"2025-09-17T01:16:17.195785+00:00"}